         <head>III Diálogos araucanos en dialecto picunche</head>
         
         <p xml:lang="arn" n="1"> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="petu" pos="AV" corresp="yet/still"><m baseForm="petu" type="particle" corresp="yet/still">Petu</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="mütrümün" pos="V" corresp="call"><m baseForm="mütrüm" type="root" corresp="call">mətü´m</m><m baseForm="nge" type="pass">ŋé</m><m baseForm="imi" type="ind2s">imi</m></w>; <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="witran" pos="V" corresp="travel/move"><m baseForm="witra" type="root" corresp="travel/move">wit’a</m><m baseForm="pu" corresp="trloc">pu</m><m baseForm="nge" type="imp2s">ŋé</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="wülngiñ" pos="N" corresp="door">ulŋín</w>-<w xml:lang="arn" lemma="mew" pos="P"><m baseForm="mew" type="P">mu</m></w>; <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="iney" pos="WH" corresp="who"><m baseForm="iney" type="particle" corresp="who">inéi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="mülen" pos="V" corresp="be"><m baseForm="müle" type="root" corresp="be">məle</m><m baseForm="iy" type="ind3">i</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="wekun" pos="AV" corresp="outside"><m baseForm="wekun" type="root" corresp="outside">wekun</m></w>. </p>
<p xml:lang="spa" n="1">Todavía llamado eres; quédate parado en la puerta; quién está afuera. </p>
<p xml:lang="span" n="1">Llaman en la puerta, vaya a ver quién es.</p>
 
         <p xml:lang="arn" n="2"> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="kiñe" pos="NUM" corresp="one"><m baseForm="kiñe" type="root" corresp="one">Kiñe</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="wentru" pos="N" corresp="man"><m baseForm="wentru" type="root" corresp="man">went’u</m></w> "<w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pen" pos="V" corresp="see"><m baseForm="pe" type="root" corresp="see">pe</m><m baseForm="a" type="fut">a</m><m baseForm="fi" corresp="3dir">vi</m><m baseForm="(ü)n" type="ind1s">n</m></w>" <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pin" pos="V" corresp="say"><m baseForm="pi" type="root" corresp="say">pi</m><m baseForm="eymew" type="ind3-2s">eimeu</m></w>.</p>
<p xml:lang="spa" n="2"> Un hombre "lo veré" te dice.</p>
<p xml:lang="span" n="2"> Un caballero quiere verte.</p>

         <p xml:lang="arn" n="3"> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="iney" pos="WH" corresp="who"><m baseForm="iney" type="particle" corresp="who">Iní</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pin" pos="V" corresp="say"><m baseForm="pi" type="root" corresp="say">pi</m><m baseForm="nge" type="pass">ŋ</m><m baseForm="ind2s">ími</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="ta" pos="DA"><m baseForm="ta" type="DA">ta</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="mi" pos="PP" corresp="your"><m baseForm="mi" type="2s">mi</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="üy" pos="N" corresp="name"><m baseForm="üy" type="root" corresp="name">qüi</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="chem" pos="WH" corresp="why/what"><m baseForm="chem" type="particle" corresp="why/what">chem</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="düngu" pos="N" corresp="thing/news/word/thought"><m baseForm="düngu" type="root" corresp="thing/news/word/thought">düŋu</m></w> <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="miawün" pos="V" corresp="wander"><m baseForm="miaw" type="root" corresp="wander">miáu</m><m baseForm="imi" type="ind2s">imi</m></w>, <w xml:lang="arn" lemma="pin" pos="V" corresp="say"><m baseForm="pi" type="root" corresp="say">pi</m><m baseForm="fi" type="3dir">vi</m><m baseForm="nge" type="imp2s">ŋe</m></w>. </p>
<p xml:lang="spa" n="3">Quién dicho eres tu nombre, qué cosa andas haciendo, dile.</p>
<p xml:lang="span" n="3">Pregúntale quién es y qué quiere.</p>
